是否適用於以言詞所為之行政處分？其理由為何？又前揭政府採購法第
75 條第 1 項第 3 款規定是否屬特別規定，而得排除行政程序法第 98 條
第 3 項規定之適用？其理由為何？（25 分）', '[]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:34:47+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "3f3af846f323", "answer_pdf_sha1": null, "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113200", "c": "315", "s": "0608", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "甲、申論題部分", "subject": "行政法", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試", "original_question_number": "二", "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "locality", "civil_category": "法制"}'::jsonb, NULL),
